      • processEmissionFines

        java.util.Map.Entry<java.util.List<Fine>,java.util.List<CameraMessage>> processEmissionFines​(java.util.List<CameraMessage> emissionMessages)
        Method that processes all CameraMessages that are linked to emission cameras and detects any emission-related violations.
        Parameters:

        Returns:

      • linkMessages

        private java.util.Map.Entry<java.util.Map<CameraMessage,CameraMessage>,java.util.List<CameraMessage>> linkMessages​(java.util.List<CameraMessage> messages)
        Method that links speeding-related CameraMessages to each other. Two messages are seen as linked when one messages describes when a car with a license plate passed one camera and later passes the second camera linked to the first camera.
        Parameters:
        messages - is a list of speeding-related CameraMessages that need to be linked
        Returns:
        a Map Entry with a Map of linked messages as its key and a list of unprocessed CameraMessages as its value
